<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@nlogozzo:matrix.org">Nick</a> says</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Parabolic <a href="https://github.com/NickvisionApps/Parabolic/releases/tag/2023.7.2">V2023.7.2</a> is here!</p>
<p>Here&rsquo;s the full changelog:</p>
<ul>
<li>Added the ability to select a download&rsquo;s audio language if more than one are available</li>
<li>Added the option to allow for only Windows-supported characters in filenames</li>
<li>Updated translations (Thanks everyone on Weblate!)

<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2023/07/twig-104/eImjztdDKEHICHrwfFVzATVH.png" alt="" />
