<h3 id="iplan">
<a class="heading-anchor" href="#iplan" hidden><svg width="16" height="16"><use xlink:href="https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#anchor"></use></svg></a>IPlan <a href="https://github.com/iman-salmani/iplan"><svg width='16' height='16'><use xlink:href='https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#link'></use></svg></a>
</h3><p>Your plan for improving personal life and workflow</p>
<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@imansalmani:matrix.org">Iman Salmani</a> announces</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://github.com/iman-salmani/iplan">IPlan 1.9.0</a> is now out!
What&rsquo;s changed:</p>
<ul>
<li>Search button and Primary menu moved to the sidebar</li>
<li>Navigation in the calendar by scroll</li>
<li>Calendar Navigation buttons removed</li>
<li>Now task changes apply to other parts of UI too. (instead of resetting them)</li>
<li>Clickable URL Links in the task description</li>
<li>Ctrl + w shortcut for closing window</li>
<li>Code refactoring, Bug fixes, and UI improvements</li>
</ul>
<p>You can get it from <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/ir.imansalmani.IPlan">Flathub</a>

<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2023/07/twig-104/hFZWWAApmCQJIknOriWPLjSt.png" alt="" />
</p>
</blockquote>


<h3 id="gnome-network-displays">
<a class="heading-anchor" href="#gnome-network-displays" hidden><svg width="16" height="16"><use xlink:href="https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#anchor"></use></svg></a>GNOME Network Displays <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gnome-network-displays"><svg width='16' height='16'><use xlink:href='https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#link'></use></svg></a>
